                            <comment id="15404623" author="tjake" created="Tue, 2 Aug 2016 19:14:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/tjake/cassandra/tree/fix-compaction-ratelimit&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;branch&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://cassci.datastax.com/view/Dev/view/tjake/job/tjake-fix-compaction-ratelimit-testall/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;testall&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://cassci.datastax.com/view/Dev/view/tjake/job/tjake-fix-compaction-ratelimit-dtest/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;dtest&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;To show the fix:&lt;br/&gt;
  I set a compaction limit of 8mb/sec&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Before fix:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt; 459.971MiB to 458.545MiB (~99% of original) in 99,556ms.  Read Throughput = 4.620MiB/s, Write Throughput = 4.606MiB/s, Row Throughput = ~298,272/s.  30,083 total partitions merged to 30,078.  Partition merge counts were {1:30073, 2:5, }
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Branch fix:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt; 459.971MiB to 458.545MiB (~99% of original) in 57,124ms.  Read Throughput = 8.052MiB/s, Write Throughput = 8.027MiB/s, Row Throughput = ~514,263/s.  30,083 total partitions merged to 30,078.  Partition merge counts were {1:30073, 2:5, }
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;p&gt;The output of compactionstats and CompactionInfo is still showing the uncompressed data size but I see no simple way to fetching the actual on disk pointer after &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-5863&quot; title=&quot;In process (uncompressed) page cache&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-5863&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-5863&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15405602" author="krummas" created="Wed, 3 Aug 2016 09:07:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;LGTM, just one minor comment;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;in &lt;tt&gt;AbstractCompactionStrategy#getCurrentCompressionRatio()&lt;/tt&gt; - should it calculate the average compression ratio instead of just getting the compression ratio for the last sstable - maybe we could use &lt;tt&gt;TableMetrics#computeCompressionRatio(Iterable&amp;lt;SSTableReader&amp;gt;...)&lt;/tt&gt;?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15406166" author="tjake" created="Wed, 3 Aug 2016 16:33:45 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I pushed an update to fix the compression ratio calc. Also, I noticed the way of calculating the size read was broken for leveled compactions since we combine many sstables into the scanner.  When a reader jumps from one sstable to another there may be big jumps which don&apos;t reflect the actual read amount.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I also added this to cleanup, verify, gc compactions. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15407824" author="krummas" created="Thu, 4 Aug 2016 14:08:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;it looks like there are a few related dtest failures:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://cassci.datastax.com/view/Dev/view/tjake/job/tjake-fix-compaction-ratelimit-dtest/lastCompletedBuild/testReport/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://cassci.datastax.com/view/Dev/view/tjake/job/tjake-fix-compaction-ratelimit-dtest/lastCompletedBuild/testReport/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15413836" author="tjake" created="Tue, 9 Aug 2016 16:56:18 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I pushed another change to address the problem and the dtests are now clean.  Will wait for your confirmation I&apos;m ok to commit.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15414837" author="krummas" created="Wed, 10 Aug 2016 07:16:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;created &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-12422&quot; title=&quot;Clean up the SSTableReader#getScanner API&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-12422&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-12422&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; for further cleanup&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
